nsive and recognized platforms in the world for digital marketing and SEO.\\n\\nfrom $117/mo\\n4.9\\n\\n#3\\n\\nMargaret by Hispatec Review\\nDiscover how Hispatec combines ERP, field management, and predictive AI in one ecosystem. Ideal for agricultural SMEs seeking full traceability.\\n\\nPrices not public\\n4.9\\n\\n#4\\n\\nLandbot Review\\nLearn how Landbot helps SMEs automate conversations and qualify leads with no-code AI chatbots. Full review covering features, pricing, and more.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.8\\n\\n#5\\n\\nNotebookLM Review\\nNotebookLM is a Google tool that combines artificial intelligence and content organization to facilitate research and document analysis.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.8\\n\\n#6\\n\\nQuickbooks Review\\nDiscover what QuickBooks offers: AI-powered automation, invoicing, bank reconciliation, and 750+ integrations. Full review of features and alternatives.\\n\\nFree trial\\n4.7\\n\\n#7\\n\\nAKOOL (videos) Review\\nAKOOL creates interactive streaming avatars and translates videos with AI lip-sync. See how it compares for customer service bots and global marketing.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#8\\n\\nHolded Review\\nHolded is a cloud-based platform designed for small and medium-sized businesses to manage their entire operation in one place.\\n\\nfrom €7.50/mo\\n4.6\\n\\n#9\\n\\nTidio Lyro AI Review\\nLyro AI is Tidio’s conversational artificial intelligence engine, designed to automatically answer frequently asked questions and reduce ticket volume on digital channels.\\n\\nfrom $29/mo\\n4.6\\n\\n#10\\n\\nSetmore Review\\nSetmore is an appointment and payment management platform that allows small and medium businesses to accept online bookings 24/7, send automatic reminders and process payments online or in person from a single panel.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#11\\n\\nRask AI Review\\nRask AI translates and dubs videos with voice cloning and lip-sync in 60+ languages. See how it helps SMEs expand globally without re-filming content.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#12\\n\\nSystran Review\\nSYSTRAN is an automatic translation tool based on artificial intelligence (AI), focused on companies needing to communicate, document or localize content in multiple languages.\\n\\ndesde $18.99/mes\\n4.6\\n\\n#13\\n\\nMindtrip Review\\nMindtrip is an AI-powered travel platform that combines inspiration, planning, and booking in one interface.\\n\\nRequest a demo\\n4.6\\n\\n#14\\n\\nSynthesia Review\\nSynthesia creates professional videos with photorealistic AI avatars in 120+ languages. Read our review of features, pricing, and free trial limitations.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#15\\n\\nMicrosoft Designer Review\\nSee how Microsoft Designer uses DALL-E to create stunning visuals integrated with your MS 365 workflow. Full review covering features, pricing, & alternatives.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#16\\n\\nYouCanBookMe Review\\nAn online appointment management tool that allows freelance professionals and even small and medium enterprises to synchronize calendars, automate confirmations & reminders, and charge when booking through Stripe.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#17\\n\\nWix Studio Review\\nWix Studio is the advanced evolution of Wix, designed for agencies, developers, and creative teams seeking a professional design platform without needing to code from scratch.\\n\\nfrom $12/mo\\n4.6\\n\\n#18\\n\\nPerplexity Review\\nPerplexity AI review: iterative research, verifiable citations, and real-time data. See if this AI tool is right for your business.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.6\\n\\n#19\\n\\nBitrix24 Review\\nBitrix24 is a comprehensive platform that combines CRM, marketing automation, project and task management, collaboration, an omni-channel Contact Center, and a website/store builder; all integrated.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.5\\n\\n#20\\n\\nIcon Review\\nIcon is an artificial intelligence platform for digital marketing that positions itself as \\\"The First AI Admaker.\\\"\\n\\nfrom $39/mo\\n4.5\\n\\n#21\\n\\nDinoRank Review\\nDinoRANK is a