plan\\n4.5\\n\\n#31\\n\\nDescript Review\\nDescript transforms video editing with text-based workflows, AI voice cloning, and studio-quality audio enhancement.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.4\\n\\n#32\\n\\nHubspot CRM Review\\nHubSpot CRM is a comprehensive platform for centralising contacts, companies, deals, and commercial communications, with Marketing, Sales, Service, Content, Data, and Commerce Hubs all in the same suite.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.4\\n\\n#33\\n\\nGoogle AppSheet Review\\nDiscover how Google AppSheet lets SMEs build mobile and web apps without code. Explore features, pricing, integrations, and AI capabilities in our full review.\\n\\nfrom $5/mo\\n4.4\\n\\n#34\\n\\nAKOOL (images) Review\\nAKOOL delivers photorealistic AI image generation and retouching for e-commerce. See how it stacks up for product photography, pricing, and SME use cases.\\n\\nFree plan\\n4.4\\n\\n#35\\n\\nZoho CRM\\nZoho CRM is a comprehensive Customer Relationship Management platform. It brings together lead capture, opportunity management, commercial automation, data analytics, and collaboration in a single environment.\\n\\nfrom €14/mo\\n4.4\\n\\n#36\\n\\nSquarespace Review\\nSquarespace is a no-code platform that allows you to create websites, online stores, and portfolios without requiring technical knowledge.\\n\\nfrom €11/mo\\n4.4\\n\\n#37\\n\\nGoogle Cloud AI Review\\nGoogle Cloud S2T is an automatic speech recognition service developed by Google, which is part of the Google Cloud platform.\\n\\nfrom $0.016/min.\\n4.4\\n\\n#38\\n\\nMS Power Automate Review\\n\\n4.4\\n\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4a6c71a4781ff05e\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"url":"https://agentaya.com/reviews/","finalUrl":"https://agentaya.com/reviews/","status":200,"contentType":"text/html","title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8f22062df43f1f9f\">>>\nSource: Web Fetch\n---\nBest AI Tools Reviews 2026 | Compare AI Software for SMEs\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8f22062df43f1f9f\">>>","extra