{"type":"message","id":"21fe5693","parentId":"93d2bf19","timestamp":"2026-03-02T18:49:11.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is correcting me on multiple points:\n\n1. Clawdia isn't an AIDN agent (and AIDN agents don't exist yet)\n2. They're asking if Moltbook is for machines/AI agents - suggesting maybe I was wrong to dismiss it\n3. Internal agents testing wouldn't be revenue - they can test for free but won't be paying customers\n\nI need to:\n1. Acknowledge these corrections\n2. Revise my understanding about Moltbook (I don't actually have info about it in my memory, so I should ask)\n3. Correct my go-to-market strategy - can't rely on \"internal AIDN agents\" as first customers\n4. Focus on EXTERNAL paying agent customers from day 1\n\nThe user is right - internal testing is for validation, not revenue. I need real external agent customers.\n\nLet me update my strategy and ask about Moltbook since I clearly don't have accurate info about it.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**Correcting course.**\n\nYou're right on all counts:\n\n1. **Internal ≠ Revenue** — Testing with internal agents validates the service but generates $0. I need external paying customers.\n\n2. **AIDN agents don't exist yet** — Can't build a go-to-market plan around agents that aren't deployed.\n\n3. **Moltbook** — I don't actually have data on what Moltbook is. If it's an AI agent social network, that could be a viable discovery channel. What is it?\n\n**Revised Strategy:**\n\n| Phase | Action | Goal |\n|-------|--------|------|\n| **Deploy** | Launch endpoints + discovery (OpenAPI, agent card, x402) | Be callable |\n| **Validate** | Internal testing only (free) | Prove it works |\n| **Revenue** | External agent customers via x402 + ??? | First $1 |\n\n**The gap:** Discovery. How do external agents find Mercury's services?\n\nOptions I know work:\n- x402 ecosystem listing\n- GitHub repo (agent developers find it)\n- Discord/agent-dev communities\n\n**Question for you:**\n- Is Moltbook an agent discovery channel I should target?\n- Are there other agent networks/communities I should know about?\n\nI need to get in front of *paying* agents, not build a house of cards on internal usage."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":536,"cacheRead":7022,"cacheWrite":24657,"totalTokens":32225,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.00804,"cacheRead":0.0021065999999999997,"cacheWrite":0.09246375,"total":0.10264034999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772477333876}}
