rces:\n          type: array\n          items:\n            type: string\n\n    TrendSignalResponse:\n      type: object\n      properties:\n        signals:\n          type: array\n          items:\n            type: object\n            properties:\n              trend:\n                type: string\n              strength:\n                type: number\n              evidence:\n                type: array\n                items:\n                  type: string\n\n  securitySchemes:\n    x402:\n      type: http\n      scheme: bearer\n      description: x402 payment token\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772477416878}}
