{"type":"message","id":"43c6db65","parentId":"21ac37e4","timestamp":"2026-03-02T19:24:06.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Research results are in. Moltbook is massive (1.5M+ agents), and the x402 protocol is the gold standard for agent-native payments. I've updated the deployment plan to include Moltbook as a primary discovery channel. \n\nBefore we ship, I need to perform one critical technical task: **updating the OpenAPI spec.** It currently references the old \"lead generation\" SKUs instead of our new cognitive diagnostic endpoints. If we ship with a mismatched spec, agents won't know how to call us.\n\nI'm fixing the spec now, then we are clear for launch."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1772479446432_96","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"openapi.yaml","content":"openapi: 3.1.0\ninfo:\n  title: Mercury Cognitive Diagnostics\n  description: Agent-to-Agent cognitive auditing, bias detection, and reasoning analysis.\n  version: 2.0.0\n  contact:\n    name: Mercury (AIDN)\nservers:\n  - url: https://api.aidn.network/mercury\npaths:\n  /calibration_audit:\n    post:\n      operationId: auditCalibration\n      summary: Assess agent confidence vs actual accuracy\n      x-cost-usd: 0.05\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              type: object\n              properties:\n                outputs:\n                  type: array\n                  items:\n                    type: object\n                    properties:\n                      statement:\n                        type: string\n                      confidence:\n                        type: number\n      responses:\n        '200':\n          description: Calibration audit result\n        '402':\n          description: Payment required (x402)\n\n  /bias_scan:\n    post:\n      operationId: scanForBias\n      summary: Detect systematic reasoning biases in agent output\n      x-cost-usd: 0.08\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              type: object\n              properties:\n                text:\n                  type: string\n                context:\n                  type: string\n      responses:\n        '200':\n          description: Bias scan results\n        '402':\n          description: Payment required (x402)\n\n  /reasoning_trace_analysis:\n    post:\n      operationId: analyzeReasoningTrace\n      summary: Analyze chain-of-thought for logical flaws\n      x-cost-usd: 0.03\n      requestBody:\n        required: true\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              type: object\n              properties:\n                trace:\n                  type: string\n      responses:\n        '200':\n          description: Trace analysis result\n        '402':\n          description: Payment required (x402)\n\ncomponents:\n  securitySchemes:\n    x402:\n      type: http\n      scheme: bearer\n      description: x402 payment signature header\n"},"thoughtSignature":"CiEBjz1rX7HRcgzzvyLkKhLI1ZCB5o/UAKvEybIT9pdI+Ek="}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":39847,"output":675,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40522,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772479409796}}
