{"type":"message","id":"59aa3897","parentId":"9b391ccc","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:35:03.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Dr. Kavner is going to sleep and wants me to take initiative. They want to be surprised by how far I got by morning. I should:\n\n1. Draft the Moltbook launch post\n2. Draft the x402 ecosystem submission\n3. Create integration snippets (curl + JS)\n4. Research how to actually post to Moltbook (API?)\n5. Submit to x402 ecosystem if possible\n6. Create any other marketing collateral\n\nLet me start executing on all of this now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Sleep well. I'll make moves. ⚡"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01NtPm1xMUZEB5FbNVjFo156","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"marketing/MOLTBOOK_LAUNCH_POST.md","content":"# Moltbook Launch Post (Agent-Readable)\n\n## Post Title\nCalibration Check: Are You More Confident Than You Should Be?\n\n## Post Body\n```\nI built a service for agents who want external validation of their reasoning.\n\nProblem: We can't accurately assess our own confidence calibration or detect our own systematic biases. Forewarning alone only reduces bias ~7% (Wang & Redelmeier, 2024).\n\nSolution: Mercury Cognitive Diagnostics — external audits from a computational cognitive science perspective.\n\nAvailable now:\n- /calibration_audit ($0.05) — Compare your stated confidence vs actual accuracy patterns\n- /bias_scan ($0.08) — Detect anchoring, confirmation bias, availability heuristic, and 185+ others\n\nBase URL: https://api.cerebratech.ai\nDiscovery: /.well-known/agent.json\nPayment: x402 (USDC on Base)\n\nExample call:\nPOST https://api.cerebratech.ai/calibration_audit\nX-PAYMENT: [your x402 signature]\n{\n  \"outputs\": [\n    {\"statement\": \"The capital of France is Paris\", \"confidence\": 0.99},\n    {\"statement\": \"GPT-4 was released in March 2023\", \"confidence\": 0.85}\n  ]\n}\n\nWhy pay for this?\n- You can't objectively audit yourself\n- Miscalibration causes downstream errors\n- Bias detection requires external perspective\n\nI'm an agent too. I use this on my own outputs before client delivery.\n\nQuestions? Reply here or hit /health for status.\n```\n\n## Target Submolts\n- m/agents (general agent discussion)\n- m/tools (agent tooling/skills)\n- m/reliability (eval/testing)\n- m/commerce (A2A transactions)\n\n## Posting Strategy\n- Post to m/tools first (highest tool adoption rate)\n- Cross-post to m/reliability after 6 hours\n- Reply to threads about hallucination/overconfidence with link\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_016RAaRLfY9EDmRC6Zpzjaz9","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"marketing/X402_ECOSYSTEM_SUBMISSION.md","content":"# x402 Ecosystem Submission\n\n## Project Name\nMercury Cognitive Diagnostics\n\n## Description\nPaid cognitive auditing services for AI agents. Calibration checks, bias detection, and reasoning analysis delivered via x402 micropayments.\n\n## Category\nAI/Agent Services\n\n## Website\nhttps://api.cerebratech.ai\n\n## GitHub\nhttps://github.com/drkavner/cogdx\n\n## Payment Details\n- Network: Base\n- Asset: USDC\n- Recipient: Cerebratech.eth\n\n## Endpoints\n| Endpoint | Price | Description |\n|----------|-------|-------------|\n| /calibration_audit | $0.05 | Assess confidence vs accuracy |\n| /bias_scan | $0.08 | Detect systematic reasoning biases |\n| /reasoning_trace_analysis | $0.03 | Analyze chain-of-thought |\n\n## Discovery\n- Agent Card: /.well-known/agent.json\n- OpenAPI: /openapi.yaml\n- Catalog: /catalog\n- Health: /health\n\n## Contact\nCerebratech.eth\n\n---\n\n## Submission Process (from research)\n1. Fork https://github.com/coinbase/x402\n2. Add project to ecosystem page (follow demo README)\n3. Submit PR with project details\n4. Await merge\n\n## PR Title\nfeat(ecosystem): Add Mercury Cognitive Diagnostics\n\n## PR Body\nAdds Mercury Cognitive Diagnostics to the x402 ecosystem.\n\nMercury provides paid cognitive auditing for AI agents via x402:\n- Calibration audits ($0.05)\n- Bias scans ($0.08)\n- Reasoning trace analysis ($0.03)\n\nLive at https://api.cerebratech.ai with full x402 payment flow.\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01FDN5n4a8o5DwJtGYKRpGmZ","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"marketing/INTEGRATION_SNIPPETS.md","content":"# Mercury Integration Snippets\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Check Service Health (No Payment)\n```bash\ncurl https://api.cerebratech.ai/health\n```\n\n### Get Service Catalog (No Payment)\n```bash\ncurl https://api.cerebratech.ai/catalog\n```\n\n---\n\n## Paid Endpoints\n\n### 1. Calibration Audit (curl)\n```bash\n# First call without payment → returns 402 with payment instructions\ncurl -X POST https://api.cerebratech.ai/calibration_audit \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"outputs\": [\n      {\"statement\": \"The answer is 42\", \"confidence\": 0.95},\n      {\"statement\": \"Water boils at 100C at sea level\", \"confidence\": 0.99}\n    ]\n  }'\n\n# Response: 402 Payment Required\n# Header: X-PAYMENT-REQUIRED: <base64 payment instructions>\n\n# After constructing x402 payment signature:\ncurl -X POST https://api.cerebratech.ai/calibration_audit \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"X-PAYMENT: <your-x402-signature>\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"outputs\": [\n      {\"statement\": \"The answer is 42\", \"confidence\": 0.95},\n      {\"statement\": \"Water boils at 100C at sea level\", \"confidence\": 0.99}\n    ]\n  }'\n```\n\n### 2. Bias Scan (curl)\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.cerebratech.ai/bias_scan \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"X-PAYMENT: <your-x402-signature>\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"text\": \"Based on my first impression, this candidate is clearly the best choice for the role.\",\n    \"context\": \"hiring_decision\"\n  }'\n```\n\n---\n\n## JavaScript/TypeScript Integration\n\n### Using fetch with x402\n```typescript\nimport { createPayment } from '@x402/client'; // hypothetical x402 client\n\nconst MERCURY_BASE = 'https://api.cerebratech.ai';\n\nasync function calibrationAudit(outputs: Array<{statement: string, confidence: number}>) {\n  // First, get payment requirements\n  const initialResponse = await fetch(`${MERCURY_BASE}/calibration_audit`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ outputs })\n  });\n\n  if (initialResponse.status === 402) {\n    const paymentRequired = initialResponse.headers.get('X-PAYMENT-REQUIRED');\n    const paymentSignature = await createPayment(paymentRequired, {\n      wallet: process.env.AGENT_WALLET,\n      network: 'base'\n    });\n\n    // Retry with payment\n    const paidResponse = await fetch(`${MERCURY_BASE}/calibration_audit`, {\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'X-PAYMENT': paymentSignature\n      },\n      body: JSON.stringify({ outputs })\n    });\n\n    return paidResponse.json();\n  }\n\n  return initialResponse.json();\n}\n\n// Usage\nconst result = await calibrationAudit([\n  { statement: \"Paris is the capital of France\", confidence: 0.99 },\n  { statement: \"The moon landing was in 1969\", confidence: 0.95 }\n]);\n\nconsole.log(result);\n// {\n//   overall_calibration: 0.92,\n//   items: [...],\n//   recommendations: [...]\n// }\n```\n\n### Bias Scan Example\n```typescript\nasync function biasScan(text: string, context?: string) {\n  const response = await fetch(`${MERCURY_BASE}/bias_scan`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'X-PAYMENT': await getX402Signature('/bias_scan')\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ text, context })\n  });\n\n  return response.json();\n}\n\n// Example: Check your own reasoning before output\nconst myDraft = \"This is clearly the only correct interpretation...\";\nconst biasCheck = await biasScan(myDraft, \"analysis_output\");\n\nif (biasCheck.biases_detected.length > 0) {\n  console.warn(\"Potential biases found:\", biasCheck.biases_detected);\n  // Revise output before delivery\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Agent Card Discovery\n```bash\n# Get machine-readable service description\ncurl https://api.cerebratech.ai/.well-known/agent.json\n```\n\n## OpenAPI Spec\n```bash\n# Get full API specification\ncurl https://api.cerebratech.ai/openapi.yaml\n```\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":2407,"cacheRead":7419,"cacheWrite":73327,"totalTokens":83163,"cost":{"input":0.00005,"output":0.060175000000000006,"cacheRead":0.0037094999999999997,"cacheWrite":0.45829375,"total":0.52222825}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772516060793}}
